Package ca.yapper.yapperapp.UMLClasses

Class User

java.lang.Object
ca.yapper.yapperapp.UMLClasses.User
public class User extends Object
The User class represents a user in the application with details such as device ID, contact information, roles, and lists of events they are associated with. This class provides methods to manage user data in Firestore and retrieve user information.

  • Constructor Details

    • User

      public User(String deviceId, String email, boolean isAdmin, boolean isEntrant, boolean isOrganizer, String name, String phoneNum, boolean isOptedOut, ArrayList<String> joinedEvents, ArrayList<String> registeredEvents, ArrayList<String> missedOutEvents, ArrayList<String> createdEvents)
      Constructs a new User with the specified attributes.
      Parameters:
      deviceId - The unique device ID of the user.
      email - The email address of the user.
      isAdmin - True if the user has admin privileges.
      isEntrant - True if the user has entrant privileges.
      isOrganizer - True if the user has organizer privileges.
      name - The name of the user.
      phoneNum - The phone number of the user.
      isOptedOut - True if the user has opted out of notifications.
      joinedEvents - List of event IDs the user has joined.
      registeredEvents - List of event IDs the user has registered for.
      missedOutEvents - List of event IDs the user missed out on.
      createdEvents - List of event IDs the user created.
